name: Cave Painting (30/08/2021 CIEN)
description: An artwork in the Cave Painting Series by the artist M Plummer-Fernández. Created and minted 30/08/2021. This cave is the second in the series combining Generative Art techniques created in 2012-2015 with AI. The Cave Paintings are produced by a custom neural network system that projects visions onto imaginary caves in response to prompts chosen by the artist.
